    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Testing techniques that cause minimal damage to the sample. The designation is the middle term in characterizing destructivity of scientific analysis, falling between ‘destructive testing’ and 'non destructive testing’.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
